				<td colspan="2"><span>From <a href="http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=bardbalance&amp;message.id=3150#M3150">developers thread</a>
<br />
<blockquote><b>Quote:</b><br><span class="quote">MythraDCanta
<br />

<br />
The bard community would appreciate it if you'd look into this, as we've made zero progress since completing the 1.5 quests.
<br />

<br />
Alkron Wyrmsong in Nobel's Causeway speaks of four armor pieces worn by Oshriuk. We've only been able to find three.
<br />

<br />
Black Chaos Gauntlets (Nobel's Causeway)
<br />
Black Chaos Boots (Wall of Slaughter)
<br />
Black Chaos Breastplate (Riftseekers)
<br />

<br />
We are still missing the Black Chaos Greaves.
<br />

<br />
The progression is:
<br />
Causeway (gloves) -&gt; WoS (boots) -&gt; _______ (greaves) -&gt; Breastplate (riftseekers)
<br />

<br />
From this we extrapolate that the Black Chaos Greaves are meant to drop in Muramite Proving Grounds, but they have yet to be found from any common mob, raid encounter, or trial.
<br />

<br />
Again, we'd appreciate some feedback on this. Thanks~
<br />
</span></blockquote>
<br />
    Ashlanne 11.03.04
<br />

<br />
        Community Representative 
<br />

<br />
    Greetings all,
<br />

